134
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,080
We have so much catching up to do.

135
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:07,990
Why are you hiding?

136
00:09:09,270 --> 00:09:10,110
Come out.

137
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,600
Meet Mr. Yan.

138
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:18,840
Chuang.

139
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,230
