140
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:25,440
Nothing.

141
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:29,510
Just that your man is following me now.

142
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,960
You should learn

143
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:33,750
